OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with some
OL,6,Flong sunny spells through the day.
OL,7,FVery warm with light winds, but
OL,8,Fslightly breezier on the east coast.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA dry, warm and bright
OL,11,Fevening with hazy sunny periods. It
OL,12,Fwill then remain dry for the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night with clear spells and light
OL,14,Fwinds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FDry with early morning
OL,17,Fcloud soon burning off to leave a warm
OL,18,Fday with sunny spells. Fresher on the
OL,19,Feast coast with the risk of patchy low
OL,20,Fcloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
