OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FPartly cloudy but warm on Thursday and
OL,7,FFriday with the risk of heavy and
OL,8,Fthundery outbreaks of rain. Occasional
OL,9,Fhaar for coastal areas. Fresher by
OL,10,FSaturday.
